WEBVTT

00:13:27.033 --> 00:13:30.992
but to feel her lungs filled
while she has them.

00:13:32.786 --> 00:13:33.983
Priorities change.

00:13:35.556 --> 00:13:38.027
Or Kate -- she just wants to know

00:13:38.051 --> 00:13:42.086
her dog Austin is lying
at the foot of her bed,

00:13:42.110 --> 00:13:45.827
his cold muzzle against her dry skin,

00:13:45.851 --> 00:13:48.574
instead of more chemotherapy
coursing through her veins --

00:13:48.598 --> 00:13:49.779
she's done that.

00:13:50.849 --> 00:13:55.865
Sensuous, aesthetic gratification,
where in a moment, in an instant,

00:13:55.889 --> 00:13:59.241
we are rewarded for just being.